      "While sitting on her throne, Hela remembers that when Odin was king, she was his executor, and now that she is the queen, Skurge will be her executor. Meanwhile, Heimdall sneaks into the dome of the Bifrost and steals the sword that activates the Bifrost. It is revealed that Heimdall has been slowly organizing a resistance against Hela. Without the sword, Hela cannot complete her conquest in all realms, so she sends her soldiers to hunt this resistance.",
